1.2.name: wordpress/free-stock-photos-foter
1.2.description:
Foter is the easiest and fastest way to add Creative Commons photos to your blog. We find and host millions of photos from many online sources and make them available to be included in your blog posts.

This plugin lets you seach, manage and add Creative Commons photos to your blog posts in a very simple way.

Some of the features:

  • Image resizing: flexibility and preview feature

  • Image download: you can use plugin or simply download image from foter.com website

  • Attribution info: all attribution information is automatically added to the photo, so you don't need to add it manually

  • Search photos: you can search photos by tags or keywords

  • Speed: very fast and easy to use

Website: Free Stock Photos Foter.com
